Class DomainTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.rdm.DomainTypes

  • public class DomainTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    Domain Type enumeration values, see RDM Usage Guide for domain model definitions (DMT = DomainType). This will be extended as new message types are defined and implemented.
